1 has a request to hold in custody from another jurisdiction within
2 the state, the defendant may post a bond in the other jurisdiction
3 to release the hold. Upon proof that a bond has been posted, the
4 request to hold in custody from the other jurisdiction shall be
5 released.
6 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
7
8 COMMITTEE REPORT BY: COMMITTEE ON JUDICIARY AND PUBLIC SAFETY
